about.summary: A pure-Python robots.txt parser with support for modern conventions

name: protego
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "Protego" %}
{% set version = "0.1.16" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: a682771bc7b51b2ff41466460896c1a5a653f9a1e71639ef365a72e66d8734b4

build:
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"
  number: 0

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - six

test:
  requires:
    - pytest
  source_files:
    - tests
  commands:
    - pytest tests

about:
  home: https://github.com/scrapy/protego
  license: BSD 3-Clauses
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: A pure-Python robots.txt parser with support for modern conventions

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - Gallaecio
